---
title: Warm and Rustic Pear Cobbler Serves 2 | Perfect for company or just for yourself
description: This rustic dessert is lovely enough to serve for guests but you'll probably want it all to yourself! If you've got some vanilla ice cream lying around, scoop some to serve alongside for extra decadence!
